    "causal_summary": "Manual test scenarios for graph-signal-activation need structured per-phase documentation instead of relying on scattered playbook rows. Phase 010 covers 15 graph-focused scenarios spanning typed degree scoring, co-activation boost, causal depth signals, community detection, graph rollback and explainability, and feature-flag-driven graph lifecycle features, so reviewers need one packet that preserves the mapped feature links, acceptance criteria, and evidence expectations for each test.",
